fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 jumped 165.95 points or 0.92% to settle at 18,255.80. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, fell 0.90% to 11.73. HDFC Bank, Housing Development Finance Corporation (HDFC) and Reliance Industries (RIL) were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The May 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 25 May 2023.
